# Brook running weston-presentation-shm — a hand-written libwayland-client
# demo (no libtoytoolkit, no libcairo, no libwayland-cursor).  Fills its
# surface with a colour cycling pattern.  Useful as a visual sanity check
# that 'set vfb auto' really gives the client the full physical FB.
# Crucially, it does NOT call wl_cursor_theme_load, so it does not hit the
# pending no-XCURSOR-theme crash that takes down weston-flower/eventdemo.
set vfb auto
run /nix/store/g5c0jccsa5ws6kzf58mmwknyvzryzz2n-waylandd-brook-0.1-brook/bin/waylandd
run /nix/store/ad9dmdrrhqpz4ygqpkhr9bfcjisrlgjk-weston-weston-presentation-shm-bundle-15.0.0-bundle/bin/weston-presentation-shm
